modName: Jordi - An ECE Dark Elf Preset - DELETED
summary: Just a simple dark elf preset for ECE.
descriptionHtml:
[u]Dunmer Female - Jordi[/u]

Hello, Nexus community! This is my very first mod, so I’m extremely sorry if you come across any problems (but you hopefully won’t, as this is just a simple ECE preset).
I don’t currently have a well thought-out backstory for this character, but if this mod becomes popular enough, I will probably make one. In the meantime, thank you for taking a look at my preset! ^-^

For your character to look the way I intended, you will require:
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]SKSE[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]Enhanced Character Edit[/url] - by tktk1
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url] - by dimon99
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] - by HHaleyy
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61178/?]Adorable Face[/url] - by  Luminalion
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49279/?]Northborn Scars[/url] - by Northborn
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60730/?]HHairstyles[/url] - by HHaleyy
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty (Special Elves Edition)[/url] - by LogRaam

Installation:
1- Place the included file into the following directory : Documents\my games\skyrim\CME_save.
2- Open up Skyrim and type “showracemenu.”
3- In the “Body” tab, use the slot load to find and select slot 4.
4- Edit Jordi to your personal taste.
5- Enjoy!

Credit:
HHaley for her wonderful ECE presets (which I used to model my own).
